{"tid":2173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林祖舜稱屢違條款　第三方高登App《HKG+》將終止運作","createTime":"2016-11-25T18:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-25T19:41:53.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b37bce766cb76c96e8d7afc29b91932f9b36a94e","tid":2173,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"高登討論區是不少網民愛流連之地，其中一個供網民瀏覽網站的第三方App「HKG+」將於11月25日停止服務。不少網民對此感到可惜，並批評香港高登網站行政總裁林祖舜，官方所設App不如HKG+優勝，近日更傳出有人將另起爐灶，設新討論區。林祖舜向《香港01》指，HKG+觸犯部份條款而決定終止合作。但林亦稱，高登與HKG+「相信都會有合作空間」。<br />\n<br />\n撚同你合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7658ddf301b4b9c6e968f1f2423a1fd9d445cad5","tid":2173,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"林祖舜接受《香港01》查詢時指，高登與坊間的第三方程式合作時，有特定規條限制，但HKG+違反部份牽涉cache（高速緩存）的條款，「已經偏離本身原意&hellip;&hellip;變得愈來愈商業性」。林又形容HKG+已非單單是「閱讀器」，故決定終止有關授權。<br />\n<br />\n祖舜則指，「有無呢件事，任何人都可以搞討論區」，認為有自由百花齊放。但認為有人借HKG+名義聲稱開設討論區，則是欺騙行為「呃其他人，唔知佢想做啲咩」。"},{"pid":"5c7a955e485e56270f54cacb040282b64e346690","tid":2173,"uid":6480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3863f5526f912e1905f3c2af06759d33877ccf","tid":2173,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"我屌佢老母呀"},{"pid":"705280afa36253e63b5ca7ef1555dde04f54116b","tid":2173,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:41:53.000Z","msg":"早洩狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續攬住個靜壇啦"}]}